681	    // broader filter (any rule that produces the tag) would count facts
682	    // as injective when one rule creates them and another consumes them,
683	    // even though no SINGLE rule has both prems AND concs — adding
684	    // spurious less-atoms and breaking Fin_unique's case_2.
