691	    ///   Step1: Fr(x) → St(x, k)
692	    ///   Step2: St(x, k) → []
693	    /// No round-trip → St is NOT injective in Haskell.
694	    /// Without per-rule filter, we'd mark it injective and add a
695	    /// spurious less-atom in case_2.
